{
  "stem": "471.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So you know, if you got with your stomach-- if your stomach is hungry, when you're thinking only about that, you don't think about something else.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And eventually, even if you're not hungry, you believe you're hungry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It's all human mind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It's all in your mind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] OK?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I was working-- we were working there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But we knew everything, what's going on up there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] We saw him a few times.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He come to visit people and, you know, us and the Kabelwerker.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Oh, oh, wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I got lost.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Goth?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got lost, honey.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just a moment, just a moment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How was it-- wait a minute, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were going from the camp up there, from Goth, main camp, to the Kabelwerker.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went, and we complained to the-- what's going on, the conditions that it was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, there were trying-- they were-- not trying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were liquidating the ghetto, killing young-- young people who work on a good-- for a good company up-- up to the-- to the-- to the main camp.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he went, and he took care-- Baymer, The director of the factory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The good guy, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said to the [NON-ENGLISH], I remember that was the headquarter from the gestapo.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had permission to build few barracks [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] on the property of the Kabelwerker.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they built barracks on Kabelwerker for 300 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Half were woman, and half were men.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
